# Snakemake Workflow

Thanks to the anvi'o implementation of Snakemake we can run many commands sequentially and/or simultaneously. There is plenty of good documentation on the anvi'o website about [setting up Snakemake workflows](http://merenlab.org/2018/07/09/anvio-snakemake-workflows/) so we will refrain from any lengthy explanations.

You can see all the settings we used and [download our configs file](include/default_mg.json) or grab it from the folded code below. Some commands we chose not to run but they remain in the workflow for posterity.


::: {.cell}

```{.zsh .cell-code}
anvi-run-workflow --list-workflows
